ArtyTorrent 101-Elab Ballistix Drum Loops-WAV samples
-----------------------------------------------------

Ballistix comes as a double CD with audio and WAV versions of 1750 samples.
The subtitle "Phatboy beats and Chemical Treats" is a good description of the content. Useful for industrial music as well as big beat and breakbreat, running at 135-140 bpm.

This torrent just contains drum loops with variations and fills. Future packs will have the remainder of the samples, including bass loops and oneshots.

Torrent contains 1 RAR with 458 loops
-------------------------------------

All files are normalized and acidized 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz.
